metadata.title: Lemspum Compatible Solid Stainless Steel Chain Links Band Quick Release Replacement for YAMAY SW022,Fossil Gen 5 Carlyle Smartwatch
features: Compatible: The metal bands Compatible with YAMAY SW022, Letscom GT01 smartwatch. Also compatible with AGPTEK LW11, Letsfit IW1 and SM Galaxy watch 3 45mm.

Material: The strap and the quick fit clip are made of premium stainless steel, smooth finish, comfortable and waterproof, which enhances the durability of the watchband, no sharp edges hurt your wrist.

Size: Fits wrists with a circumference of 5.5in-7.5in.The tool kit will be included to help you easily adjust the band's length to wear. Change your watch's look and feel ,the secure buckle protect it from slipping off, fits great and more securely when you are biking or working out.
Unique Design: Equipped with quick fit clip, just swap, click, easy to switch, and always secure. And the clip is metallic, you won't worry the clip is easy to rust or pop off.
Warranty: 1 Year warranty. Unconditional REPLACEMENT or REFUND for any quality issue. Life time friendly customer service. Note: Only replacement quick fit metal watch strap, NO watch.
